How founders can think about their media strategy as they grow.
Let=E2=80=99s start with one of the most jarring aspects of Techno-Optimist=
ic Media: it=E2=80=99s explicitly, unabashedly biased. Sounds bad. But ever=
y other modern media organization is biased, too, whether they admit it or =
