color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20p=
x 0;"><span>The confusing thing is that while many of the same organization=
s &#8211; from </span><em>The New York Times </em><span>to NBC &#8211; are =
