 style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margi=
n: 0 0 20px 0;">Before there&#8217;s even a company, there&#8217;s an idea.=
 You can workshop it, write about it, build prototypes, do market research,=
